list.item:
There are several points on which we must expect our other Manila Pact
                            partners to query us on in the next two or three weeks. These are: 
                                a.

When the Council should hold its first meeting;
                                b.

Level of representation;
                                c.

Where the Council should meet;
                                d.

How, organizationally, we envisage implementing Article V of
                                    the Treaty providing for military and other planning;
                                e.

Economic cooperation as provided in Article III.
